        <script>
          function addSocialIframe(el){
            el.setAttribute('data-cookiecategory', 'social');
            el.parentNode.setAttribute('data-cookie-placeholder', 'Nutné povolit cookies pro sociálni sluby');
            el.setAttribute("data-src", el.src);
            el.removeAttribute("src");
          }

          function addSocialScript(el){
            el.setAttribute('data-cookiecategory', 'social');
            el.setAttribute('type', 'text/plain');
            el.parentNode.setAttribute('data-cookie-placeholder', 'Nutné povolit cookies pro sociálni sluby');
          }

          document.querySelectorAll('iframe').forEach(function(el){
            if(el.src.length > 0){
              if(el.src.indexOf("facebook.com") !== -1){
                addSocialIframe(el);
              }
              else if(el.src.indexOf("youtube.com") !== -1){
                addSocialIframe(el);
              }
              else if(el.src.indexOf("platform.twitter.com") !== -1){
                addSocialIframe(el);
              }
              else if(el.src.indexOf("open.spotify.com") !== -1){
                addSocialIframe(el);
              }
              else if(el.src.indexOf("instagram.com") !== -1){
                addSocialIframe(el);
              }
            }
          });
          document.querySelectorAll('script').forEach(function(el){
            if(el.src.length > 0){
              if(el.src.indexOf("instagram.com") !== -1){
                addSocialScript(el);
              }
              else if(el.src.indexOf("platform.twitter.com") !== -1){
                addSocialScript(el);
              }
            }
          });

        </script>
